OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fwith cloud increasing from the north
OL,7,Fand east, perhaps a little drizzle
OL,8,Fover the hills overnight. Clear spells
OL,9,Fremaining around Lochaber and southern
OL,10,Fareas of the Great Glen.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMost of the cloud thinning and
OL,13,Fclearing during the morning with
OL,14,Fbright or sunny spells developing.
OL,15,FFeeling warm in the sunshine, but
OL,16,Fremaining cooler and cloudier near the
OL,17,Fnorth coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
